7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Chatfuel and Freshdesk (Freddy AI) share a solid foundation of core features including Ai Chatbot, Analytics, Multichannel, Automation. On the other hand, Freshdesk (Freddy AI) uniquely offers Live Chat and Ticket Management and Knowledge Base and Voice Support, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Chatfuel holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Freshdesk (Freddy AI) scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Freshdesk (Freddy AI) comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Chatfuel begins at $14.39/mo. Freshdesk (Freddy AI) stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Chatfuel requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
